Princella Adubea (amụrụ na 27 Disemba na afọ 1998) bụ onye Ghana na-agba bọọlụ nke na-agba ọsọ dị ka onye na-agbachitere Spanish Racing de Santander na ndị otu bọọlụ ụmụ nwanyị nke Ghana
Ọ nọchitere anya Ghana na ọkwa U20 na iko mba ụwa abụọ na 2016 na 2018
Ọ gbara bọọlụ maka Sporting de Huelva.
Adubea malitere ọrụ ya na klọb Techiman Ampem Darkoa Ladies na afọ 2014
N'afọ 2016, ọ duuru klọb ahụ gaa na Ghana Women's Premier League maka oge 2015 na 16 mgbe o meriri ndị mmeri Hasaacas Ladies site na otu goolu na asọmpi ikpeazụ

Ọ gbara goolu iri na itoolu n'egwuregwu iri na otu iji pụta dị ka onye kacha gbaa goolu n'oge ahụ. Ọ mechikwara oge ahụ dị ka onye kacha gbaa goolu na afọ 2016 Ghana Women's FA Cup. O meriri SWAG Female footballer of the year site na ịkụ aka na asọmpi site na Elizabeth Addo na Sandra Owusu-Ansah.

O nyeere klọb ahụ aka ijide aha Premier League ha site n'ịgba otu goolu na asọmpi ikpeazụ nke Championship na Baba Yara Sports Stadium megide Lady Strikers. Ọ gbara goolu iri na isii iji chekwaa ihe nrite ya kachasị mma ma merie ya n'oge abụọ n'usoro.
